seatuya
=======

A C wrapper library for tuyapp, providing a pure C API for local Tuya
smart-device communication.  Supports protocol versions 3.1, 3.3, 3.4,
and 3.5.

Building
--------

    ./fetch-deps.sh        # fetches tuyapp (and jsoncpp if not installed)
    autoreconf -fi
    ./configure
    make
    make check
    make install

Dependencies are fetched on demand by fetch-deps.sh — nothing is shipped
in the repository.  System-installed libraries are preferred when available.

Dependencies
------------

- tuyapp (fetched automatically into deps/)
- jsoncpp (system or fetched automatically)
- OpenSSL (system)
- A C99 compiler
- A C++14 compiler (for building tuyapp internals)
- GNU autotools (autoconf, automake, libtool) for building from git

